code: @Override public boolean equals(Object o) {     if (this == o)         return true.     if (o == null || getClass() != o.getClass())         return false.     final GetSslCertificatesResponse that = (GetSslCertificatesResponse) o.     return Objects.equals(this.certificates, that.certificates). }

public static GetSslCertificatesResponse fromXContent(XContentParser parser) throws IOException {     List<CertificateInfo> certificates = new ArrayList<>().     XContentParserUtils.ensureExpectedToken(XContentParser.Token.START_ARRAY, parser.nextToken(), parser::getTokenLocation).     while (parser.nextToken() != XContentParser.Token.END_ARRAY) {         certificates.add(CertificateInfo.PARSER.parse(parser, null)).     }     return new GetSslCertificatesResponse(certificates). }
